{"tid":2250782,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"悼念周梓樂逝世四個月 四學生涉藏無線對講機被控","createTime":"2020-10-20T10:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T13:01:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f626f35ac9ba3d074a1081b0b60de5e2b4f0f08","tid":2250782,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"近300名市民於科大生周梓樂墮樓事件四個月當日，前往出事的尚德邨悼念，當晚大批警察在將軍澳區內向市民搜身，其間四名學生於港鐵調景嶺站內疑被搜出無線對講機，分別被控無牌管有無線電通訊器具罪，今午於觀塘裁判法院提堂。主任裁判官徐綺薇應辯方要求，將案件押後至12月1日，讓辯方索取文件及法律意見。各人准以現金1,000元保釋外出，其間須每周向警方報到一次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/EYLMQVG7RFFV7HTFIF5XUJT22M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2FEYLMQVG7RFFV7HTFIF5XUJT22M%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=1e52297f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201020%2FEYLMQVG7RFFV7HTFIF5XUJT22M%2F&h=9484fd48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201020/EYLMQVG7RFFV7HTFIF5XUJT22M/</a>"},{"pid":"6a2aefbc42ed1e73dac87f415b3646f0855e56cc","tid":2250782,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd2ce4e06d5f54b7f43e56580c19b4e0da0fdcd","tid":2250782,"uid":253016,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"管有無線電通訊器具罪<br />\n殖民地式惡法"},{"pid":"2320696c15fa5b60c17c97bdc506f346ddc31c9b","tid":2250782,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6fd2ce4e06d5f54b7f43e56580c19b4e0da0fdcd","tid":2250782,"uid":253016,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"管有無線電通訊器具罪<br />\n殖民地式惡法"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:38:56.000Z","msg"